11:25.733 --> 11:27.700
[ Exhales sharply ]

11:29.433 --> 11:31.833
Oh, God.

11:31.833 --> 11:34.067
[ Siren wailing in distance ]

11:34.067 --> 11:36.833
[ Indistinct conversations,
telephone ringing ]

11:36.833 --> 11:38.567
Vicky, I want to keep you
on motive.

11:38.567 --> 11:40.233
Just dig up financials,
relationship --

11:40.233 --> 11:41.600
whatever we can get
on the guy.

11:41.600 --> 11:44.333
So, I hear you have an ID
on your victim.

11:45.067 --> 11:46.333
Take it away, Jordan.

11:46.333 --> 11:48.300
Sure.
[ Clears throat ]

11:52.067 --> 11:53.800
Leonard Walsh, sir.

11:53.800 --> 11:56.333
Did a stint in the Midlands
for child sex abuse.

11:56.333 --> 11:58.200
He came back here
after he was released.

11:58.200 --> 11:59.600
He was on the streets
within a year.

12:00.167 --> 12:01.467
Gonna be a long list of people

12:01.467 --> 12:03.067
who wanted to harm a man
like that.

12:03.633 --> 12:05.467
Good work.
Charlie, a word.

12:09.200 --> 12:11.267
I'm sorry to do this,
but I'm gonna have to move

12:11.267 --> 12:13.367
a couple of your people over
to the Kayleigh Connor case.

12:13.367 --> 12:15.433
Of course.
Uh, I understand.

12:15.433 --> 12:16.833
Sir.

12:20.233 --> 12:22.867
It's my mother.
She's been assaulted.

12:22.867 --> 12:24.400
[ Down-tempo music plays ]

12:24.400 --> 12:27.067
[ Birds chirping ]

12:27.067 --> 12:28.833
Uh-huh.

12:28.833 --> 12:30.500
Okay.

12:34.800 --> 12:36.067
What's wrong?

12:36.067 --> 12:38.367
That was your father.

12:39.067 --> 12:40.800
Your granny's coming to stay.

12:42.800 --> 12:45.367
[ Music continues ]

12:46.333 --> 12:48.733
Oh, Harry.
Are you okay?

12:48.733 --> 12:51.200
Look. Don't worry.
I'm not gonna fuss.

12:51.200 --> 12:54.133
I'm afraid you've missed Lola.
She's staying at a friend's.

12:54.133 --> 12:55.533
I'm quite tired.

12:55.533 --> 12:57.800
I might just go to bed
if that's all right.

12:57.800 --> 13:00.433
Yeah. Of course.
Um...

13:00.433 --> 13:02.067
I'll bring your case in.

13:02.067 --> 13:03.233
[ Door opens ]

13:03.233 --> 13:05.200
-Shout if you need me.
-[ Door closes ]

13:05.200 --> 13:07.333
Is she okay?

13:07.333 --> 13:09.633
She'll be fine.
You know my mother.

13:14.767 --> 13:16.367
[ Exhales deeply ]

13:16.367 --> 13:19.467
[ Dog barking, vehicles passing
in distance ]

13:21.067 --> 13:22.867
[ Exhales, inhales sharply ]

13:22.867 --> 13:26.500
[ Sighs ]
Shit.

13:28.833 --> 13:31.067
I couldn't hear her.

13:31.067 --> 13:32.567
I've got a meeting first thing,
but I can always --

13:32.567 --> 13:34.067
That's not necessary.

13:34.067 --> 13:35.600
Hi, Granny.

13:37.667 --> 13:39.200
Are you okay?

13:39.200 --> 13:41.433
Yes, dear.
I'm fine.

13:44.067 --> 13:47.467
Look, I don't want you all
rearranging your lives.

13:48.167 --> 13:52.067
