13:52.067 --> 13:54.067
[ Down-tempo music plays ]

13:55.233 --> 13:58.167
[ Birds chirping ]

14:17.333 --> 14:19.767
[ Music continues ]

14:35.167 --> 14:39.067
You can piss right off,
you little shit!

14:40.600 --> 14:43.067
Oh, that was delicious.

14:43.067 --> 14:44.267
I've eaten too much.

14:44.267 --> 14:47.433
Well, I told you
not to have thirds.

14:48.567 --> 14:50.367
[ Exhales deeply ]

14:52.567 --> 14:56.633
Actually, uh, Harry, we don't
allow smoking in the house.

14:56.633 --> 14:58.267
Why do you have an ashtray,
then?

14:58.267 --> 14:59.567
Uh, we don't.

14:59.567 --> 15:01.200
Yeah, you do.
Over there.

15:01.200 --> 15:02.233
[ Gasps ]

15:09.067 --> 15:11.233
