about the state of my morality

15:24.767 --> 15:27.200
rather than my health.

15:27.200 --> 15:29.800
If you're that keen
to get rid of me...

15:29.800 --> 15:32.267
Of course not.
Just asking.

15:32.767 --> 15:34.667
Well, I-I'm not gonna lie.

15:34.667 --> 15:37.300
This whole thing's been
very stressful.

15:38.800 --> 15:41.167
Actually, Lola,
you might be able to help.

15:41.167 --> 15:42.767
Your school's a little rough,
isn't it?

15:42.767 --> 15:44.800
I'm sure you can get your hands
on some decent weed.

15:44.800 --> 15:46.067
-CHARLIE: Mother.
-Oh.

15:46.067 --> 15:47.433
Don't they call it weed
anymore?

15:47.433 --> 15:50.133
