16:25.333 --> 16:27.733
Mm.
Tell me about it.

16:27.733 --> 16:29.267
[ Laughs ]

16:29.267 --> 16:31.067
[ Down-tempo music plays ]

16:31.067 --> 16:33.267
[ Dog barking ]

16:51.733 --> 16:53.833
[ Music continues ]

17:10.467 --> 17:13.200
