20:17.767 --> 20:20.567
[ Voice breaking ]
If anyone has any information...

20:20.567 --> 20:21.867
NEWSCASTER:
That was Kevin Connor.

20:21.867 --> 20:23.167
You're sure about this, Harry?

20:23.167 --> 20:24.733
It's an automatic
five-year sentence

20:24.733 --> 20:26.267
